{"tid":1724957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非仲可以點走落去？(長文）","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T15:55:01.000Z","uid":185259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c99b5e3d9575dd247945ed4cb58fa6d16b0476","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"此post非割蓆post  只是個人意見<br />\n老實說 我本人覺得運動到咗樽頸<br />\n好多人對身邊發生嘅事 盲目<br />\n或者極嬲但無奈感好強<br />\n香港人愈來愈敏感 好容易情緒化<br />\n勇武都不斷地起事 換來嘅係手兄被捕傷亡<br />\n<br />\n好多人唔認同暴力 但制度暴力更可怕<br />\n相信呢個係民間共識<br />\n即使做法不敢苟同 但理念永遠一致<br />\n咁先有唔割蓆出現<br />\n作為一個和非理 無力感非常之重<br />\n一方面想做啲嘢 但我唔敢做前線<br />\n<br />\n其實政府就係睇中呢一點<br />\n犯法、恐懼 法律套係我地身上<br />\n但老實講 每個人心中唔多唔少都有啲驚<br />\n日日就比啲黑警全副武裝係街恐嚇<br />\n再衰啲就拉你返去為所欲為<br />\n邊個唔驚 分分鐘冇命<br />\n但係 甘心過呢啲日子咩<br />\n我唔係藍絲 唔識美化制度嘅惡行<br />\n<br />\n社會撕裂係一個事實<br />\n但我相信香港人係有愛<br />\n天琦講唔好被仇恨支配<br />\n因為愛同團結先係政府最驚<br />\n可能遊行集會你會話已經無用<br />\n又鬧啲人成日用二百萬人打飛機<br />\n但我 真係想用我嘅方式去抗爭<br />\n講明各有各做 就等勇武抖下<br />\n當如果一次又一次都係咁行都冇回應<br />\n勇武嘅話語權會更大更深<br />\n<br />\n我唔知啲大台、民陣嗰啲仲會唔會搞<br />\n但如果有 我一定會行<br />\n當然警謊一定會好多藉口<br />\n同埋你會話之前咪試過 咪反對咗 咪又tg放題<br />\n但我想講 一次唔得就試夠一百次<br />\n宜家唔試 就係代表你冇做嘢<br />\n我都係想見到咁多日抗爭中<br />\n仲會有一日係可以有愛團結<br />\n<br />\n可能以上嘅都係廢話 但都係真心<br />\n總之 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"13881fe8b3bd3e97cba906c02877371c50a06e14","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"2236a7fe15ca3873074a7bb88c63f12e11b0e5b2","tid":1724957,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"63bbee85aecc41ae941991e00bddae4821da46de","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fb047e86d865c7011dc58dcdc0fc146de058935","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35547b44796e8edb79f7208ec7caae1003b21bcb","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce145d235cbed803618d9038025258ad6ff0f858","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f81f7f0df14d462f51ca308eafdef49a6142158","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af5598b6026d9ec4f4b5c0388d84fd140c609271","tid":1724957,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecaf3ccd2d87185fe7d4412c828297461121253","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:21:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd94d0996b110ab153e5a2ec8beb9bfbfe4a861e","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"988f698f0e6db7af20c04101273d72dbcaa768e9","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e721ec8cec361fc5261c31bfb8205bbf0a6ff052","tid":1724957,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"1d49157de740e8eee415de70c462692d2bcccb17","tid":1724957,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"611e477d62aac3440d5906ac787cb09d673b00c9","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e285fbce739bb29db2e5208dd53349fc830f3674","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"690e28e3c5a0eb45815582a09fa6269b8a86acfa","tid":1724957,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"極權利用恐懼來管治"},{"pid":"306fe2f2f9ae9aa65f22ac28b3d726769a5ce133","tid":1724957,"uid":21057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b00ba90846aafdff357ae317bb882c8bf251773b","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f13b5f9a7bc5a4d5b64a1d99295b1cd90b9cde8b","tid":1724957,"uid":185259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"690e28e3c5a0eb45815582a09fa6269b8a86acfa","tid":1724957,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"極權利用恐懼來管治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"呢個先係要行出嚟嘅理由"},{"pid":"22a35486dff00c486bfe31a